<% extend '_flow-no-banner' %>

<% block 'head_end': %>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= @__asset('shopify-partner.css') %>">

<% end %>

<% block 'page_flow': %>

<section class="section landing js-home">
  <div class="landing__baner">
    <div class="landing__baner-content container">
      <div class="landing__logo-shopify js-banner-content">
        <img src="<%= @__asset('img/logo-shopify.png') %>" alt="">
      </div>
      <p class="landing__baner-detail">
        At NTQ Solution, our dedicated team of Shopify designers and developers build customised, enterprise solutions
        for fast growing, high volume merchants. With offices in Sydney and Melbourne, we specialise in multi-channel
        retail and work with some of Australias leading brands. WithShopify Plus, your business is guaranteed seamless
        growth and scalability.
      </p>
      <p class="landing__baner-detail">
        Our core value is to create profitable eCommerce business for our clients. Whether youâ€™re starting small or
        scaling up, we provide strategy, design and growth services to maximise your commerce.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="landing__why-shopify--title">Why shopify</h3>
  <div class="landing__why-shopify">
    <div class="landing__why-shopify--content">
      <div class="landing__why-shopify--avata" style="background-image: url(<%= @__asset('img/everything-handled.jpg') %>);"></div>
      <div class="landing__why-shopify--wrapper">
        <div class="landing__why-shopify--text">
          <h3 class="landing__why-shopify--title-detail">Everything's handled</h3>
          <p class="landing__why-shopify--detail">Concentrate on growing your business. Shopify has everyhing built-in
            and taken care of by professionals. Your store will be fast, secure, and taken care of.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="landing__why-shopify--content">
      <div class="landing__why-shopify--avata" style="background-image: url(<%= @__asset('img/mobile-app.jpg') %>);"></div>
      <div class="landing__why-shopify--wrapper">
        <div class="landing__why-shopify--text">
          <h3 class="landing__why-shopify--title-detail">Mobile app and shopify Pos</h3>
          <p class="landing__why-shopify--detail">Take your business everywhere with the mobile app, or seamlessly grow
            into a robust point of sale system to power your retail locations.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="landing__why-shopify--content">
      <div class="landing__why-shopify--avata" style="background-image: url(<%= @__asset('img/robuss-app.jpg') %>);"></div>
      <div class="landing__why-shopify--wrapper">
        <div class="landing__why-shopify--text">
          <h3 class="landing__why-shopify--title-detail">robust app marketplace</h3>
          <p class="landing__why-shopify--detail">There's always an app for that. With over 1,800 apps in the App
            Store,
            we use them to power everything from email marketing to accounting integration.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="landing__why-shopify--content">
      <div class="landing__why-shopify--avata" style="background-image: url(<%= @__asset('img/cross-channel.jpg') %>);"></div>
      <div class="landing__why-shopify--wrapper">
        <div class="landing__why-shopify--text">
          <h3 class="landing__why-shopify--title-detail">cross channel selling</h3>
          <p class="landing__why-shopify--detail">Your online store is only one of the channels available for you to
            sell
            on. Sell on Facebook, Amazon, Ebay, and Buzzfeed ? with more channels being added all of the time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="landing__why-shopify--content">
      <div class="landing__why-shopify--avata" style="background-image: url(<%= @__asset('img/endless.jpg') %>);"></div>
      <div class="landing__why-shopify--wrapper">
        <div class="landing__why-shopify--text">
          <h3 class="landing__why-shopify--title-detail">endless customization</h3>
          <p class="landing__why-shopify--detail">If you can think it, we can build it. Shopify's liquid language lets
            us create beautiful responsive websites that will create a lasting impression.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="landing__service container">
    <h3 class="landing__service-title">Our Shopify Service</h3>
    <div class="landing__service-content">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <div class="landing__service-item--app landing__service-item">
            <p class="landing__service-item--title">Platform migration</p>
            <div class="overlay"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="landing__service-item--content">Take your performance to the next level with our re-platform
            services to Shopify and Shopify Plus.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <div class="landing__service-item landing__service-item--business">
            <p class="landing__service-item--title">Start a store</p>
            <div class="overlay"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="landing__service-item--content">We take care of everything from start to launch so you can focus on
            building your business. Our Shopify developers take the beautiful work done by our designers and bring it
            to life. It's our job to build dazzling sites without sacrificing functionality or speed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <div class="landing__service-item landing__service-item--service">
            <p class="landing__service-item--title">Managed services</p>
            <div class="overlay"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="landing__service-item--content">Regardless of the size of your project, whether it be small design
            work or an ongoing project that requires monthly support, NTQ can shape up your venture to make it a
            fruitful experience that will improve your eCommerce business.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="landing__ready">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="landing__ready-content">
        <div class="landing__ready-text">
          <h3 class="landing__ready-title">Ready to get your Shopify store?</h3>
          <h4 class="landing__ready-detail">Send us a message and we'll get back to you as soon as possible</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="landing__ready-btn">
          <a href="#">Get in touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<% end %>
